title: (Tues Early) Lunchbox Rehearses Acting Scenes with Bobby + What We’d Auction off From our Personal Biggest Accomplishments + Mailbag: Husband Lied About Vasectomy
itunes:title: (Tues Early) Lunchbox Rehearses Acting Scenes with Bobby + What We’d Auction off From our Personal Biggest Accomplishments + Mailbag: Husband Lied About Vasectomy
description:
Lunchbox may have an acting role. Bobby revealed last week that he got him an audition. So in order to prepare, they act out some famous scenes to see if he has what it takes. We share what things from our personal life we would auction off to make the most money. In the mailbag, a husband wants to come clean after lying to his wife about getting a vasectomy.
